[h3]How to use[/h3]
[list]
[li]Download the fwl.mjs module and import it in the file where you're going to write the document and bind it to global object[/li]
[li]In case of node[/li]
[li] call fwl(global)[/li]
[li]If you use a browser[/li]
[li] call fwl(window)[/li]
[li]Set the document type to print[/li]
[li]Call create method and inside braces use the functions you need to generate the code.[/li]
[/list]
[code="javascript"]import fwl from "./fwl.mjs";
fwl(global);
documentType = "bbcode"; //"markdown" "html"

[/code]
